data.description: BELOW TAX VALUE!  New Roof, new paint and new siding on this beautiful 2,800 sq foot home on a cul-de-sac with fenced back yard in Taras Trace subdivision.  Large and open floor plan with fantastic kitchen, granite counter tops, full length cabinets, perfect for entertaining or a big family.  Main level has LVP flooring, gas fireplace and a huge family room.   A massive 22+ foot primary bedroom and walk in closet welcome you home after a long day.  Large private back yard with storage building perfect for grilling out with family and friends or just relaxing/enjoying the privacy of a fenced back yard.  This home is located just 2 miles from Interstate 40 and is within walking distance to Statesville Soccer complex, Statesville Fitness and community walking trails and playgrounds.  Seller is offering a home warranty.
